00:20:04.205 --> 00:20:05.339 position:38% line:83% align:start
[BATOU]
Uh?

00:20:05.373 --> 00:20:06.274 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MOTOKO]
Batou?

00:20:06.307 --> 00:20:09.443 position:19% line:83% align:start
