00:21:28.657 --> 00:21:31.258 position:33% line:83% align:start
Whoa, wait!
Put those down!

00:21:42.036 --> 00:21:44.171 position:35% line:83% align:start
[ISHIKAWA]
The hostages' cyberbrains.

00:21:44.205 --> 00:21:45.906 position:13% line:89% align:start
They've been contaminated!

00:21:45.940 --> 00:21:47.975 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MOTOKO]
