00:21:58.018 --> 00:21:59.954 position:7% line:83% align:start
[ISHIKAWA] All right, got it.
Found the intruder.

00:21:59.987 --> 00:22:01.656 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MOTOKO]
That's the host for the virus.

00:22:01.690 --> 00:22:04.626 position:27% line:83% align:start
