our resources to combat it.

01:26:44.246 --> 01:26:46.415 position:10% line:83% align:start
You're doing the same thing
with your badges and guns.

01:26:46.448 --> 01:26:48.817 position:19% line:83% align:start
Even if you don't see
yourself as a criminal,

01:26:48.851 --> 01:26:50.586 position:21% line:83% align:start
that doesn't change
the fact that you breed them

01:26:50.619 --> 01:26:52.955 position:16% line:89% align:start
for the sake of profits.

01:26:52.988 --> 01:26:56.325 position:35% line:83% align:start
[AMAGATA]
You'll understand someday.

01:27:17.279 --> 01:27:18.947 position:21% line:89% align:start
[FAKE MOTOKO gasps]

01:27:18.981 --> 01:27:20.316 position:27% line:89% align:start
[MOTOKO grunts]

01:27:27.423 --> 01:27:28.957 position:21% line:89% align:start
[FAKE MOTOKO grunts]

01:27:48.143 --> 01:27:50.479 position:10% line:89% align:start
So that's where you've been.

01:28:03.959 --> 01:28:05.961 position:33% line:83% align:start
[CARETAKER]
You're late.

01:28:05.994 --> 01:28:08.130 position:19% line:89% align:start
She's leaving us now.

01:28:31.621 --> 01:28:33.155 position:30% line:89% align:start
[MOTOKO gasps]

01:28:37.059 --> 01:28:38.394 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MOTOKO]
Kurutsu!

01:28:40.262 --> 01:28:42.231 position:24% line:83% align:start
[CHRIS (KURUTSU)]
Kurutsu is dead.

01:28:42.264 --> 01:28:44.534 position:16% line:83% align:start
Even if I could control
that body again,

01:28:44.567 --> 01:28:48.337 position:19% line:83% align:start
